'''美国军事初级院校'''（'''Military Junior College'''，简称'''MJC'''<ref name="GoArmy">{{cite web |url=http://www.goarmy.com/rotc/courses-and-colleges/military-colleges.html |title=MILITARY COLLEGES |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=GoArmy |accessdate=5 March 2014}}</ref>）是提供[[提前授衔计划|提前授衔计划]]且特别被《[[美国法典|美国法典]]》[[美国法典第10条|第10条2107(a)]]所承认的[[军事化|军事化]][[初级学院|初级学院]]<ref name="GPO">{{cite web |url=https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/USCODE-2010-title10/html/USCODE-2010-title10-subtitleA-partIII-chap103.htm |title=U.S.C. Title 10 |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=United States Government |accessdate=9 April 2017}}</ref>。军校学员通过这一途径可以在两年内获得获得[[副学士学位|副学士学位]]并成为[[美国陆军|美国陆军]][[预备役|预备役]]部队的[[少尉|少尉]][[军官|军官]]，但若想成为现役军官则仍需完成[[学士学位|学士学位]]<ref name="GoArmy"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.marionmilitary.edu/about/ |title=About MMI |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Marion Military Institute |accessdate=5 March 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。除了陆军的军事课程外，有的学院亦开设[[美国空军|空军]]、[[美国海军陆战队|海军陆战队]]等其他军种的初期军事课程<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.marionmilitary.edu/programs/plc-overview.cms |title=A FEW WILL LEAD |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Marion Military Institute |accessdate=5 March 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.marionmilitary.edu/programs/airforce-overview.cms |title=U.S. Air Force ROTC |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Marion Military Institute |accessdate=5 March 2014 }}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，有的则含有下辖的联邦军校预科项目或高中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vfmac.edu/academy/ |title=Academy |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Valley Forge Military Academy |accessdate=5 March 2014}}</ref>，还有的除军校学员外也对外招收一般大众甚至[[留学生|留学生]]，针对他们提供一般初级学院课程<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gmc.cc.ga.us/page.php?page_id=2020 |title=International Student Admissions |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Georgia Military College |accessdate=5 March 2014}}</ref>。美国的初级军事院校一共有四所，他们分别是[[佐治亚军事学院|佐治亚军事学院]]、[[马里昂军事学院|马里昂军事学院]]、{{Link-en|新墨西哥军校|New Mexico Military Institute}}和{{Link-en|弗吉谷军校|Valley Forge Military Academy and College}}<ref name="GoArmy"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amcsus.org/page.cfm?p=64&filter_data8=&filter_data44=1&filter_data17=&filter_data18=&key=&submit=SEARCH |title=Directory of Military Schools & Military Colleges |author= |date=unknown |work= |publisher=Association of Military Colleges and Schools of the United States |accessdate=5 March 2014}}</ref><ref name="ABCNews">{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/missouri-military-academy-dating-1880-close-46675858 |title=Missouri military academy dating to 1880 will close |author=the Associated Press |date=unknown |work= |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=9 April 2017 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170410214029/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/missouri-military-academy-dating-1880-close-46675858 |archivedate=2017年4月10日 }}</ref>。

当国家处于总动员状态时，一般大学预备军官训练团将会暂停，但军事初级学院也不会因此受到影响，还是按其正常模式培养少尉军官<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.apd.army.mil/epubs/DR_pubs/DR_a/pdf/web/r145_1.pdf |title=Army Regulation 145–1 Senior Reserve Officers’ Training Corps Program: Organization, Administration, and Training |accessdate=2017-08-01 |date= |page=6 |publisher=U.S. Army |work=U.S. Army |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2017-08-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801201040/http://www.apd.army.mil/epubs/DR_pubs/DR_a/pdf/web/r145_1.pdf }}</ref>。

